00:03:27.422 --> 00:03:30.690
Well once again I'm assuming
you've had a go at it.

00:03:30.690 --> 00:03:32.820
And the key realization here is that this

00:03:32.820 --> 00:03:35.174
negative one to the k plus
two this makes this whole

00:03:35.174 --> 00:03:36.435
thing either positive or negative.

00:03:36.435 --> 00:03:38.514
The denominator is going to be positive.

00:03:38.514 --> 00:03:40.826
Well it's definitely going
to be positive for all

00:03:40.826 --> 00:03:43.089
the ks frankly for
which the principal root

00:03:43.089 --> 00:03:44.691
