00:04:32.547 --> 00:04:35.135
So square root of k plus one so we can

00:04:35.135 --> 00:04:36.904
get this out of the denominator.

00:04:36.904 --> 00:04:39.990
And let's actually multiple
both sides times 1,000

00:04:39.990 --> 00:04:42.023
because this is a thousandth
