00:05:03.629 --> 00:05:07.312
We could square both
sides and we get 1,000,000

00:05:09.065 --> 00:05:13.344
is less than or equal to k plus one.

00:05:13.344 --> 00:05:17.304
And then we can just
subtract one from both sides

00:05:17.304 --> 00:05:21.855
